cc:Work.dc:title: Timezones of the World
cc:Work.dc:description:
This is a public domain work, CC0 1.0 Universal http://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/ Created by Mark Warren 2013
Data from the public domain tz_world_mp shapefile as of 2012-10-08 by Eric Muller as published at http://efele.net/maps/tz/world/
Timezone guidelines data from the public domain ne_10m_time_zones shapefile published by Natural Earth at http://www.naturalearth.com
Composited using kbh3rd's shptosvg.pl utility https://github.com/kbh3rd/shptosvg/wiki
shptosvg.pl -x 2048 -y 1024 -p1 -d0.5 -T "+proj=longlat +ellps=WGS84 +datum=WGS84 +no_defs" \ tz_world_mp,srs="+proj=longlat +ellps=WGS84 +datum=WGS84 +no_defs",group=TZID,same=TZID \ ne_10m_time_zones,srs="+proj=longlat +ellps=WGS84 +datum=WGS84 +no_defs",group=iso_8601

cc:Agent.dc:title: Mark Warren, Eric Muller, Natural Earth, github's kbh3rd, Roger Oger
